Educational Reflections: How University Examinations Make "Academic Bullies" and "Academic Dregs" Work in Their Place - Xinhuanet
Three students from Lanzhou Jiaotong University wrote a letter to the university leadership, reflecting their confusion about the university examination, and proposed to improve the difficulty of the examination, change the type of examination questions, so that the examination truly reflects the actual level of students.
Indeed, college exams have long been a hot topic.
On university campuses, students come from all over the world, with different levels of ability, and with different levels of learning, the learning situation is very different.
It is inevitable that there will be different feelings in the assessment of groups with such diverse characteristics.
Of course, if the test question type is single, the repetition rate is high, the question is too simple, will inevitably cause another very different feeling.
Students who do not work hard may be able to pass the exam by concentrating on the assault, if they think of other ways, it is possible to achieve twice the result with half the effort.
In this way, there will be "learning slag" usually do not invest can pass, or even get a high score; "learning bully" usually never fall out of class, homework, notes are good, the examination is not much higher than the "strange status quo".
In this way, Lanzhou Jiaotong University students reflect the problems in the university examination is not for nothing, I believe that this situation is not only Lanzhou Jiaotong University.
In this sense, I would like to praise the three students who wrote directly.
In fact, people who have gone to university are aware that it is not uncommon to prepare for the test, think of various ways to "take" the test questions from the teacher, strive to draw the scope of the test, and get "key guidance" before the test, even in the test with a small copy, after the test for the teacher's high hand is not a strange story.
In my opinion, as a kind of teaching quality assessment guidance, to measure whether a university examination is qualified or not depends more on the teacher's comprehensive grasp of teaching and learning, and on the scientific proposition on this basis.
At the undergraduate level, majors begin to be subdivided, and many major courses are based on basic knowledge.
There is no doubt that whether a comprehensive grasp of the basic knowledge of a subject, is the content of the university examination to examine.
Undergraduate knowledge is basically the basic theory of the subject and basic common sense, from the point of knowledge, the space for change is not big, basically fixed.
As one teacher said, "20 years ago, I studied the basics of college mathematics, but I'm still learning it, and I'm still focusing on it."
But the knowledge point is basically the same, does not mean that the test question type is single, the test question is repeated.
In many universities, the examination is usually composed of a question group, and then the senior teacher of the subject co-ordinates the composition of the examination paper, and the examination review is also attended by all the teachers who undertake the subject, so as to overcome the duplication of the examination questions to a certain extent.
But to draw up a set of test questions in line with the actual teaching and learning, the questions according to the overall situation of students' learning, difficult and normal distribution, but also need to comprehensively grasp the teaching situation, a comprehensive analysis of the degree of students' learning, so that the test proposition on the difficult and dynamic grasp of the question type, not only can highlight the basic knowledge, but also take into account the ability to test, and innovative design of the question type.
Examination is the baton of university education, what kind of examination, students will have the corresponding test preparation program, in the long run, will affect the effectiveness of university education.
Lanzhou Jiaotong University attaches great importance to the student's letter of recommendation, and has deployed a rectification plan in the whole school.
All teaching units are required to organize teachers to carry out seminars and self-examination of the final examination, formulate examination paper propositions and related systems, and strengthen the supervision and inspection of examination paper propositions and audit links, refine the assessment of grades, and strengthen the comprehensive assessment of all aspects of curriculum teaching.
From the mechanism to solve the problem of single type of test questions, repeated questions and so on is the issue that the university examination affairs need to face, of course, need to introduce the corresponding system, but the effort is expensive in the daily, need teachers to fully grasp the teaching situation, not only to understand the teaching content, but also to understand the students' learning situation, both sides to understand, teaching and learning will be better docking, form a benign interaction, the examination will be more in line with reality, so that the "student bully" and "student slag" in their respective places.
